'''flyadeal'''（{{lang-ar|طيران أديل}}）是[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]的[[低成本航空公司|低成本航空公司]]，總部設於[[阿卜杜拉·阿齊茲國王國際機場|阿卜杜拉·阿齊茲國王國際機場]]，為[[沙烏地阿拉伯航空|沙烏地阿拉伯航空]]旗下的[[子公司|子公司]]。該航空公司於2017年9月23日開始營運國內航班。

== 歷史 ==
沙烏地阿拉伯的[[國家航空公司|國家航空公司]]沙烏地阿拉伯航空於2016年4月17日宣布將成立flyadeal<ref>{{cite press release |date=2016-04-18 |title=Saudia Airlines announces launching flyadeal, a new low-cost carrier |url=http://aaco.org/media-center/news/aaco-members/saudia-airlines-announce-launching-flyadeal-a-new-low-cost-carrier |publisher=[[阿拉伯航空運輸組織|Arab Air Carriers Organization]] |access-date=2016-04-20 |language=en |archive-date=2016-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421113446/http://aaco.org/media-center/news/aaco-members/saudia-airlines-announce-launching-flyadeal-a-new-low-cost-carrier |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gulfnews">{{cite news |date=2016-04-18 |title=Saudia launches low cost Flyadeal airline |url=http://gulfnews.com/business/aviation/saudia-launches-low-cost-flyadeal-airline-1.1715397 |newspaper={{tsl|en|Gulf News|海灣新聞|Gulf News}} |location=Dubai |access-date=2016-04-20 |language=en |archive-date=2018-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180114133631/http://gulfnews.com/business/aviation/saudia-launches-low-cost-flyadeal-airline-1.1715397 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ch-aviation.com/portal/news/45573-saudia-unveils-new-budget-carrier-flyadeal |title=Saudia unveils new budget carrier, flyadeal |date=2016-04-18 |website={{tsl|en|ch-aviation|ch-aviation}} |access-date=2016-04-20 |language=en |archive-date=2016-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419221758/http://www.ch-aviation.com/portal/news/45573-saudia-unveils-new-budget-carrier-flyadeal |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其為沙烏地阿拉伯航空集團SV2020轉型策略（Saudia Group's SV2020 Transformation Strategy）的一部分，該策略的目的是在2020年以前將集團的各單位提升至一定等級。而flyadeal的目標客群是沙烏地阿拉伯國內旅客、前往[[朝覲_(伊斯蘭教)|朝覲]]和[[副朝覲|副朝覲]]的[[穆斯林|穆斯林]]等。<ref name="hanware">{{cite news |last=Hanware |first=Khalil |date=2016-04-19 |title=Flyadeal's launch puts Saudia at higher altitude |url=http://www.arabnews.com/economy/news/912581 |newspaper=[[阿拉伯新聞|Arab News]] |location=Jeddah |access-date=2016-04-20 |language=en |archive-date=2017-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171230022427/http://www.arabnews.com/economy/news/912581 |dead-url=no }}</ref>flyadeal於2017年9月23日正式開通航班，往返[[吉達|吉達]]和[[利雅德|利雅德]]。<ref name="chav25sep2017" />

